OL,3,CBurst pipe leaves thousands of homes
OL,4,Cwithout clean water
OL,6,FThousands of residents across parts of
OL,7,FLeicestershire and in Nuneaton are
OL,8,Fcurrently without clean tap water.
OL,10,FIt's after a leak caused a widespread
OL,11,Foutage issue.
OL,13,FThe incident is affecting homes in:
OL,15,F"It is chaos"
OL,17,FResidents are also being warned of low
OL,18,Fpressure and having discoloured tap
OL,19,Fwater.
