OL,3,CBurst pipe leaves thousands of homes
OL,4,Cwithout clean water
OL,6,FSome have reported flooding in the
OL,7,FLeicester Lane area of Desford, near
OL,8,Fto Bosworth Academy.
OL,10,FOne resident said "There is a big
OL,11,Fflood in Desford. Halfway down Station
OL,12,FRoad and all the way down the hill to
OL,13,Fthe railway. Severn Trent are there
OL,14,Fbut it is chaos."
OL,16,FSevern Trent Water teams are in the
OL,17,Farea investigating a burst pipe.
